snippet.title: Diana plays Hide and Seek with Disney Princess Dolls Video for kids
snippet.description:
Diana plays Hide and Seek with Disney Princess Dolls Video for kids
Diana in the dress of Princess Belle is looking for #Princess Disney dolls: Rapunzel, Cinderella, Aurora, Tiana, Jasmine, Snow White, Pocahontas, Ariel, Belle... The dolls of the princess hid, but Diana found everyone!  Video for #kids
